text: Södertörns Simsällskap is a Swedish swim team founded in 1967. The club's activities take place in Eriksdalsbadet, Torvalla simhall and Vårbyhallen. The most famous swimmer is Sarah Sjöström. ==Swimmers== *Stefan Nystrand (-2006) *Louise Jöhncke *Simon Sjödin *Sarah Sjöström ==External links== *Södertörns SS's official homepage Category:Swimming clubs in Sweden Category:Sports clubs established in 1967 Category:Sporting clubs in Stockholm Category:1967 establishments in Sweden
